The seed taken in dark wine clears away phlegm and nausea. Sextius Niger says that mallows are injurious to the stomach; the T heban lady Olympias that with goose-grease they cause abortion‚ and others that a handful of their leaves taken in oil and wine assist the menstruation of women.
